                            <p>For additional information with regards to our use of Google products, click&nbsp;<a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites">HERE</a>.</p>
                            <p><strong>Please note that there might be additional cookies of our third-party advertising partners used in our website – all as detailed in the cookie notification and management tool that will be displayed once you access our website, and subject to applicable law in your jurisdiction.</strong></p>
                            <p><strong>Opt Out:</strong></p>
                            <p>You may easily opt-out of our website’s data collection, sharing process and targeted advertising services by following the instructions below:</p>
                            <p>You may set your browser to block all cookies, including cookies associated with our website, or to indicate when a cookie is being used by us, by adjusting the privacy and security settings of your web browser. Please refer to the support page of&nbsp;your browser to learn more about how you can adjust your privacy and security settings. The
